      "para_id": "Q004967.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the god of his land , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , presented this ( seal ) to Lu-Enlila , the sea mechant , his servant ."
    }
